{
  "stem": "22883.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because when I was going from my place where I was living-- Podravska-- to Warsaw, where I was working, I had to pass along on the side of the ghetto, of the ghetto wall.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when the-- this uprising was taking place, I have seen the-- the-- the-- the smokes from burning houses and the-- and the shooting and so on.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It made a-- a terrible impression on me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It-- well, maybe my impression were-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] were different than other people because the people, other Polish people were quite-- well, to-- to some extent, indifferent.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I-- that's what I'm saying.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's very hard.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But [SIGHS] I felt some kind of pity, some kind of-- of sorrow that's happened to-- to those people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was not anti-Semite.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I told you the-- the few episodes when I was treated like a Jew.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So somehow I had-- I was-- somehow I felt that I'm involved in that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And at the very beginning, Liliana didn't-- well, she was at that time very pretty, well, relatively very pretty.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I was not [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in love from first sight.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was not impressed about her beauty.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "What I was impressed in her, that was her intellectual side.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I-- I was impressed about that she knew about movies, about the literature, and so on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But [SIGHS] not, I would say, not like a boy is impressed by-- by a girl because of her beauty or something.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And my decision, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it seems to me, was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that I wanted to do something different than the rest of people, of my people, Polish people.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I-- I had some urge to-- not to recompensate, but to give the example that I could be different.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
